Package groupproject

Class Menu

java.lang.Object
groupproject.Menu
All Implemented Interfaces:
Indexable
public class Menu extends Object implements Indexable
Menu entity Implements methods to view menu, create, update and remove both product and promotional product Reads stored menu from text file upon instantiation, writes to text file every time menu are created/ deleted or updated.
Author:
Teresa Zhang
